      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Refimprove|date=November 2007}}
{{Infobox Anatomy |
  Name         = Cervix |
  Latin        = cervix uteri |is a '''[[madison page kendra schaaf]]'''
  GraySubject  = 268 |
  GrayPage     = 1259 |
  Image        = Scheme_female_reproductive_system-en.svg |
  Caption      = Schematic frontal view of female anatomy |
  Image2       = Female_reproductive_system_lateral_nolabel.png |
  Caption2     = 1: [[fallopian tube]], 2: [[urinary bladder|bladder]], 3: [[pubic bone]], 4: [[g-spot]], 5: [[clitoris]], 6: [[urethra]], 7: [[vagina]], 8: [[ovary]], 9: [[sigmoid colon]], 10: [[uterus]], 11: [[Fornix vaginae|fornix]], 12: cervix, 13: [[rectum]], 14: [[anus]] |
