      <comment>[[WP:CHECKWIKI]] error fixes + [[WP:GENFIXES|general fixes]] using [[Project:AWB|AWB]] (7707)</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox writer &lt;!-- for more information see [[:Template:Infobox writer/doc]] --&gt;
| name=C. S. Forester
| image=
| birth_date  = {{Birth date|df=yes|1899|8|27}}
| birth_place = [[Cairo, Egypt]]
| death_date  = {{death date and age|df=yes|1966|4|2|1899|8|27}}
| death_place = [[Fullerton, California]], U.S. 
| occupation = novelist
